column3: Text
Who are you?
I'm Thanos bringer of darkness
I don't know anyone by that name. Are you sure that's your name?
Yes. I'm not from around here.
Oh. Well, this is a really nice place. You should stay a bit.
Maybe. How long have you lived here?
I don't know.
You don't know?
Mm. Does it really matter?
I guess not.
Nice meeting you.
Same here.
You know this place isn't real, right?
What are you talking about? You sound crazy. Heh.
I mean, this isn't real life.
Oh, sure. And I'm your great-aunt Linda!
This is a dream.
What? You mean like in Inception? You must watch too many movies.
You made this place up to deal with your loneliness.
Man. You must have had too many drinks or something. You should lie down.
What if I could prove it to you?
If you can prove to me the world I've been living in for ten years is false, I'll give you all my money.
Okay, fine. How about this? Can you tell me where you lived before this?
Before this? I'm not sure what you mean.
Before this town. You must've moved from somewhere...
That's silly. You know, you're really funny. We could be friends.
Where did you come from?
Jesus. I don't know.
Doesn't that strike you as odd
Not particularly.
Seriously.
Listen here. It was funny at first, but now it's just getting tiring.
I'm not joking.
Hey. You're making me a bit worried. Maybe go home and lie down or something. Seriously. Goodbye.
